import React from 'react'
import { View, Text, StyleSheet } from 'react-native'
import COLORS from '../../assets/colors/colors'
import * as Icons from "react-native-heroicons/solid";


export default function Item() {
    return (
        <View >
            <View style={styles.main}>
                <View style={{ flexDirection: 'row', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', margin: 10 }}>
                    <View style={{ height: 60, width: 70, backgroundColor: COLORS.red, }}>

                    </View>
                    <View style={{ justifyContent: 'center', paddingRight: 30 }}>
                        <Text style={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>Chicken Burger</Text>
                        <Text>Spicy chicken burger</Text>
                        <Text>Taste great and beyond</Text>

                    </View>
                    <View style={{ top: 20 }}><Text>  <Icons.PlusCircleIcon style={{ color: COLORS.green }} /></Text></View>
                </View>


            </View>

            <View style={styles.main}>

            </View>
            <View style={{ backgroundColor: COLORS.main, width: '95%', borderRadius: 5, height: 70, marginTop: 12 }}>

            </View>

            <View style={{ backgroundColor: COLORS.alternate, width: '95%', borderRadius: 5, height: 70, marginTop: 12 }}>

            </View>
        </View >
    )
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    main: {
        backgroundColor: COLORS.white,
        width: '95%',
        borderRadius: 5,
        height: 85,
        marginBottom: 12
    }
})
